  "StockRole": "Close Assault",
  "YangsThoughts": "Clan Ice Hellion took the old Coriolis design and rebuilt it from the ground up using Clan tech in 2888. Lighter, faster, more dangerous. The Ultra AC/20 alone makes it something you take seriously, but stacking an LB-10X and Ultra AC/5 on top of that means it can threaten targets at almost any range. Nearly every Clan ran these as second-line units before the Invasion. Finding one in our bay means we pulled something genuinely rare out of the field.",
